Description_lang: Casting $?a137017[Wildfire Bomb]?a137016[Aimed Shot][Kill Command] reduces the cooldown of Intimidation and Binding Shot by ${$s1/1000}.1 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Casting Kill Command reduces the cooldown of Intimidation and Binding Shot by 0.5 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Lanzar Matar reduce 0.5 s el tiempo de reutilización de Intimidación y Disparo vinculante.
description_blz.pt_BR: Lançar Comando para Matar reduz em 0,5 s a recarga de Intimidação e Disparo Aprisionador.
description_blz.de_DE: Das Wirken von 'Tötungsbefehl' verringert die Abklingzeit von 'Einschüchterung' und 'Bindender Schuss' um 0,5 Sek.
description_blz.en_GB: Casting Kill Command reduces the cooldown of Intimidation and Binding Shot by 0.5 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Al lanzar Matar, se reduce 0,5 s el tiempo de reutilización de Intimidación y Disparo vinculante.

description_blz.ko_KR: 살상 명령 시전 시 위협 및 구속의 사격의 재사용 대기시간이 0.5초만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 施放擊殺命令會使威嚇和禁錮射擊的冷卻時間縮短0.5秒。
description_blz.zh_CN: 施放杀戮命令会使胁迫和束缚射击的冷却时间减少0.5秒。
